{"id": 57793, "date": "2025-07-20T04:00:33", "date_gmt": "2025-07-20T11:00:33", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57793"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T11:01:17", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T18:01:17", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-20-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/20/kingdom-of-days-july-20-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 20"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1969:\u00a0</strong>Child plays their last of six consecutive nights at the Pandemonium in Wanamassa, New Jersey. On this night, however, the band isn&#8217;t the center of attention: during Bruce&#8217;s performance, Neil Armstrong lands and walks on the moon. That&#8217;s tough for anyone to compete with, and the band takes issue with the distracting televisions placed around the club. They won&#8217;t play this club again.</p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street band play their third of six consecutive two-shows-nightly gigs at Max&#8217;s Kansas City in New York, with the Wailers as the opening act.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>A red-letter (and red-eyed) day for Bruce and the E Street Band: after a marathon nineteen-hour rehearsal that ends at 3am, and after recording work on &#8220;Jungleland&#8221; that continued until 10am, the band races to the Palace Theater in Providence, Rhode Island, for the opening night of the Born to Run Tour and Steven Van Zandt&#8217;s debut as a member of the E Street Band.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/l6IwxpL-ZDk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8Hoz79azVDI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28411\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-07-20-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-20.png?fit=692%2C1748&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"692,1748\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-07-20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-20.png?fit=119%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-20.png?fit=405%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28411 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-20.png?resize=692%2C1748&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"692\" height=\"1748\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-20.png?w=692&amp;ssl=1 692w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-20.png?resize=119%2C300&amp;ssl=1 119w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-20.png?resize=405%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 405w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-20.png?resize=608%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 608w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 692px) 100vw, 692px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>The opening stand of the Reunion Tour&#8217;s U.S. leg continues with Night Three at the Continental Airlines Arena in East Rutherford.</p>\n<div id=\"v-DhJGQnGP-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/DhJGQnGP?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19725\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-07-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?fit=2072%2C1579&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2072,1579\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1999-07-20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?fit=300%2C229&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?fit=758%2C577&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19725 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?resize=758%2C578&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"578\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?w=2072&amp;ssl=1 2072w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?resize=300%2C229&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?resize=1024%2C780&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?resize=768%2C585&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?resize=1536%2C1171&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-07-20.png?resize=2048%2C1561&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2005:\u00a0</strong>Bruce brings his solo acoustic tour to Bridgeport, Connecticut, where he tour premieres &#8220;All That Heaven Will Allow&#8221; and &#8220;Nothing Man,&#8221; both on electric piano.</p>\n<div id=\"v-wpRIRm41-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/wpRIRm41?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/L9XCvwdwCVk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2008:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their last European Magic show, at Camp Nou in Barcelona, tour premiering &#8220;I&#8217;m Goin&#8217; Down&#8221; (the first time that song has ever been played in Europe).</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SzMNhfqCOJ8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-sWVYJ29B-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/sWVYJ29B?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2011:\u00a0</strong>Bruce takes Evan to see U2 at the New Meadowlands Stadium, where Bono pays tribute to Clarence and outros from &#8220;Moment of Surrender&#8221; into &#8220;Jungleland.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dtmUsQjADjc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2013:\u00a0</strong>Bruce tour debuts &#8220;Nebraska&#8221; (as the fourth song in a <em>Nebraska </em>mini-set) and &#8220;Fade Away&#8221; when the Wrecking Ball Tour stops at King&#8217;s Hall in Belfast. Early fans get an extra treat: short but remarkable pre-show featuring a rare outing for &#8220;Maria&#8217;s Bed.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZG9JFy-hfXA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1_hpEKd65z8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NCHozP7MWBw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6DDpfU3KZas?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QW8yABgfBAc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/N8_Te_3hzjc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>The revived River Tour moves on to Horsens, Denmark, where Bruce opens with a tour premiere of &#8220;Dream Baby Dream&#8221; in memory of songwriter Alan Vega, who died four days prior. Other tour premieres include &#8220;You Never Can Tell,&#8221; &#8220;Frankie&#8221; and &#8220;Follow That Dream.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/M7VBOp1OrEM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Dt04fcJgQTM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/aGeP38rHcSI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ibvtobZFKNE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2025:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a surprise on-stage appearance with Zach Bryan at MetLife Stadium, performing with Zach and Caleb Followill\u00a0 on &#8220;Atlantic City&#8221; and returning for an encore of &#8220;Revival.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/E1V0ncuInHc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/q5hRp-yoQjQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>On this date: Steven Van Zandt makes his E Street Band debut as the Born to Run tour gets underway.  Plus: he may be the best at capturing a crowd&#8217;s attention, but even Bruce can&#8217;t compete with a moon landing.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 11383, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [2], "tags": [1306, 711, 644, 1303, 1304, 340, 674, 829, 783, 932, 610, 1305, 412, 360, 173, 630, 129, 367, 160, 728, 273, 26, 543], "class_list": ["post-57793", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-kingdom-of-days", "tag-alan-vega", "tag-all-that-heaven-will-allow", "tag-barcelona", "tag-born-to-run-tour"